frames.caption: A whimsical scene features miniature construction workers interacting with a large fried egg. The workers, dressed in orange safety vests and yellow helmets, appear to be salting the egg and inspecting it closely. The egg's yolk is vibrant and glossy, contrasting with the crispy edges of the white.
frames.description: This imaginative scene depicts tiny construction workers on a giant fried egg, creating a playful and surreal atmosphere. The setting is a close-up view of the egg in a frying pan, with steam rising, suggesting it's freshly cooked.
